    "body": "This added in #3154 because of the uncertainty as to whether when requesting a Beacon root if it was pre or post 4844 fork.\r\n\r\nNote, it is a SHOULD.\r\n\r\nI do see that it seemingly accidentally casts the net wider than maybe intended. The ResourceUnavailable component of that line could be just limited to if the Root request was past the 4844 epoch boundary\r\n",
